Well, he picked the wrong guy for that too.

523
01:19:23,771 --> 01:19:27,816
My partner is a belligerent asshole,
with his back against the wall.

524
01:19:29,401 --> 01:19:30,694
Right now, so am I.

525
01:19:31,987 --> 01:19:34,197
If I don't set this straight,
I'm in big trouble.

526
01:19:38,243 --> 01:19:40,119
Any idea where he might be?

527
01:19:43,748 --> 01:19:44,832
Mexico.

528
01:19:44,832 --> 01:19:47,626
Or maybe it was Balise.

529
01:19:51,129 --> 01:19:52,255
Really?

530
01:19:59,137 --> 01:20:01,556
I was excited about this whole thing.

531
01:20:02,557 --> 01:20:04,058
My name on a car!

532
01:20:05,142 --> 01:20:06,936
I mean, look how beautiful.

533
01:20:08,103 --> 01:20:10,314
I wanted to see my name on this thing.

534
01:20:12,983 --> 01:20:15,068
I think we would've made a go with this business.

535
01:20:31,208 --> 01:20:33,043
Don't worry.

536
01:20:33,085 --> 01:20:33,877
That's it.

537
01:20:33,919 --> 01:20:37,547
It's done.
There is no pain, its over. Its over.

538
01:28:09,878 --> 01:28:11,838
I think this has gone on long enough.

539
01:28:13,632 --> 01:28:15,759
You see any reason for this to continue?

540
01:28:17,886 --> 01:28:19,595
What do you say we meet?

541
01:28:22,890 --> 01:28:24,392
Why would I wanna do that?

542
01:28:25,976 --> 01:28:26,769
Well...

543
01:28:26,810 --> 01:28:30,522
You, me and your girlfriend
are the only players left.

544
01:28:30,564 --> 01:28:32,774
How's that for a reason?

545
01:28:35,277 --> 01:28:36,194
When?

546
01:28:37,237 --> 01:28:38,279
Tomorrow.

547
01:28:39,614 --> 01:28:40,782
There's a place on Sherman Way...

548
01:28:40,823 --> 01:28:43,034
there's a restaurant called "The Great Wall".

549
01:28:43,075 --> 01:28:43,909
You know it?

550
01:28:44,869 --> 01:28:46,120
I'll find it.

551
01:29:13,061 --> 01:29:14,312
Can I talk to you?

552
01:29:17,565 --> 01:29:18,942
I won't keep you long.

553
01:29:24,196 --> 01:29:26,031
I have to go somewhere now.
I don't think I can come back.

554
01:29:38,376 --> 01:29:42,421
Just getting to be around you...
was the best thing that ever happened to me.

555
01:30:34,928 --> 01:30:36,221
Did you bring the money?

556
01:30:42,810 --> 01:30:44,353
Here's what I'm prepared to offer...

557
01:30:45,646 --> 01:30:47,481
You give me the money,
the girl is safe.

558
01:30:48,607 --> 01:30:51,777
Forever, nobody knows about it.
She's off the limits.

559
01:30:54,029 --> 01:30:55,864
I can't offer you the same.

560
01:30:57,490 --> 01:30:59,158
So, this is what I would suggest.

561
01:31:00,618 --> 01:31:02,453
We conclude our deals...
we shake hands.

562
01:31:03,829 --> 01:31:05,789
You'll start the rest of you life.

563
01:31:08,709 --> 01:31:12,587
Any dreams you have,
plans or hopes for the future;

564
01:31:12,629 --> 01:31:15,590
I think you got to put that on holds.

565
01:31:17,258 --> 01:31:19,552
For the rest of your life,
you're gonna be looking over your shoulder.

566
01:31:19,594 --> 01:31:23,764
I'm just telling you this,
'cos I want you to know the truth.

567
01:31:25,599 --> 01:31:26,934
But the girl is safe.

568
